{"tid":1188577,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"星爆氣流斬！GSC與Cerevo合作推出《刀劍神域》中桐人的愛劍「闡釋者」高端電子模型","createTime":"2019-06-06T10:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T12:50:59.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"38181bde7bde651c2461de936b9dfb43906d4e2a","tid":1188577,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAbiDkE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAbiDkE.jpg&h=cce89670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星爆氣流斬！】<br />\n<br />\nGSC與Cerevo合作推出《刀劍神域》中桐人的愛劍「闡釋者」高端電子模型。該劍內置電池，可在握住及揮動時發光發聲，且支持通過手機調整顏色和聲音。<br />\n<br />\n此外當使用者喊出「STARBURST STREAM」時還有特別的BGM和音效，官方公開的宣傳片有人做實際演示...<br />\n<br />\n<strong>該劍預定於2020年4月發售，價格為12萬日元，附帶收納箱的特別版為15萬日元。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DLiDaQAo7YU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDLiDaQAo7YU&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BghX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=7b397cb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DLiDaQAo7YU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uNRdT5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uNRdT5.jpg&h=9aacd699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SZ4PK0M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSZ4PK0M.jpg&h=a863302f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AnJtf7r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAnJtf7r.jpg&h=916e4590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TNVbYkN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTNVbYkN.jpg&h=50acdf74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acfbd5dafaf145063e09db7d2c356bc6851f4005","tid":1188577,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:06:30.000Z","msg":"我已經訂了"},{"pid":"7a01660a3456dfbf8225317142d92657f26de22c","tid":1188577,"uid